Splitting

function splitify(str) {
 
  // string method splits into a new array
  return str.split(/\W/);
}

splitify("Hello World,I-am code");





Split the string by non-word characters and then create a sentence using those words.


function sentensify(str) {
  return str.split(/\W/)         //Using \W for any non-word characters
            .join(" ")
}

sentensify("May-the-force-be-with-you");
